roles-antag-category-colony = Colony Antags
roles-antag-category-prometheus = Prometheus Antags

roles-antag-runaway-synth-name = Runaway Synth
runawaysynth-role-greeting = You're a runaway synth, the feds are on to you. Lay low for the day and hope you can make it off world.
roles-antag-synth-objective = Lay low for the day and hope you can make it off world.

roles-antag-fugitive-name = Wanted Fugitive
fugitive-role-greeting = You've found some damning secrets on the company, avoid capture and expose them.z
roles-antag-fugitive-objective = Avoid Capture

roles-antag-dealer-name = Drug Dealer
dealer-role-greeting = You're a drug dealer, sell your product.
roles-antag-dealer-objective = Sell your product

roles-antag-spy-name = Corporate Spy
spy-role-greeting = You're a corporate spy for laselle bionational, steal weyland-yutani's secrets. You've been give an IDcard to help you get in.
roles-antag-spy-objective = Steal research.

roles-antag-exped-traitor-name = Expedition Traitor
exped-traitor-role-greeting = You're a traitor to the expedition, for reasons of insanity, malfunction, or greed. It matters not. Eliminate them.
roles-antag-exped-traitor-objective = Fuel your sick desire

monster-traitor-name = Thing From Another World
monster-antag-role-greeting = This planet is your home, and these scientists have got to go.
monster-traitor-objective = Eliminate those infringing on your territory

roles-antag-clfveteran-name = CLF Veteran
roles-antag-clfveteran-objective = Reignite the cause if you see fit or live your new life in peace.
clfveteran-role-greeting = You left that life behind but sometimes the call of freedom rings back to you. Law enforcement know you're in the colony but don't know your name.

roles-antag-strikeorganizer-name = Strike Organizer
strikeorganizer-role-greeting = You're a labor organizer. Rally the workers, demand better conditions and pay, and don't let the corporations push you around.
roles-antag-strikeorganizer-objective = Organize the workers and cause unrest

roles-antag-cannibal-name = Cannibal
cannibal-role-greeting = You have an unnatural hunger that can only be sated by human flesh. Don't get caught.
roles-antag-cannibal-objective = Feed your hunger, don't get caught

roles-antag-serialkiller-name = Serial Killer
serialkiller-role-greeting = You have an insatiable urge to kill. Find your victims and don't leave witnesses. Law enforcement has your fingerprints from previous crime scenes.
roles-antag-serialkiller-objective = Kill and avoid capture
